Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.95,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 我出門散步 ♪\N{\reng}♪ I go out walking ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:27.29,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 沐浴午夜月光 ♪\N{\reng}♪ After midnight out in the moonlight ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:29.43,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 就像我們曾經一起做的 ♪\N{\reng}♪ Just like we used to do ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:32.00,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 我總是在前進 ♪\N{\reng}♪ I'm always walking... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他還在洗澡\N{\reng}He's in his bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  蘿絲琳\N{\reng}Hello, Rose Lynn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可以來杯茶麼  你最近怎麼樣\N{\reng}Would you like a cup of tea? How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:43.37,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 我總是午夜之後散步 ♪\N{\reng}♪ I'm always walking after midnight ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.81,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 只為找尋你的蹤跡 ♪\N{\reng}♪ Searching for you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爺  你遮遮羞吧\N{\reng}Cover yourself, for God's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,遮遮羞\N{\reng}Cover yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我去\N{\reng}Oh, fuck, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一路從蘇格蘭的格拉斯哥到劇院\N{\reng}All the way from Glasgow, Scotland,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,請歡迎一個新人歌手\N{\reng}please welcome a little girl by the name of Rose Lynn Harlan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,蘿絲琳·哈倫\N{\reng}to the Opry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,女士們  先生們  羅斯·林·哈蘭\N{\reng}Rose Lynn Harlan, ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次在納什維爾的田納西州表演\N{\reng}performing for the first time here in Nashville, Tennessee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了  去你的\N{\reng}Whoo! Fuckin'A.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  過會兒再來看你\N{\reng}Right, I'll see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候\N{\reng}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候\N{\reng}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\reng}Mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你好呀\N{\reng}Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,進來吧  小林\N{\reng}Come on, Lyle. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪裏  是要去吃魚嗎\N{\reng}Where do you think you're going, all done up like a fish supper?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪  他讓你失望了  肯定的\N{\reng}Christ, he's got you down, so he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真可怕  千萬別這樣\N{\reng}That's scary. Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,無論如何  我哪兒也不去\N{\reng}Anyway, I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你們一起吃晚飯\N{\reng}I'm having my dinner wi' yous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他那麼話嘮  你卻沉默寡言\N{\reng}He never shuts up, you never speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  你這麼沉默\N{\reng}What's going on in there, eh? Sponsored silence?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你想我嗎\N{\reng}Did you miss me, eh? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,蘿絲琳\N{\reng}Rose Lynn?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為是你媽媽呢\N{\reng}I thought you were your mum there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一年就這麼過去了  時間不等人\N{\reng}That cannae have been 12 month. The time's went in like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\reng}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  瑪麗昂\N{\reng}Hello, Marion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆都晚安\N{\reng}Night, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她挺漂亮  阿曼達\N{\reng}She looks good. Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了  她在這上面花了不少時間\N{\reng}Aye. So she should. Enough time at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:07:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,她還躺在錫紙上嗎  是的\N{\reng}Does she still lie out here on tin foil? Oh, aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她穿著比基尼曬日光浴\N{\reng}One peek of the sun and that one's in a bikini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,前幾天她吃我的黃油  你的黃油\N{\reng}Other day she was in after my butter. Your butter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,身上到處都是  這很正常  瑪麗昂\N{\reng}Puts it all over her. It's natural, Marion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是個面包捲  那就再正常不過了\N{\reng}Aye, natural if you're a roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗今晚本來要過來看你\N{\reng}Mary was gonna come tonight to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她的關節炎很嚴重  所以\N{\reng}but she's awful bad with her arthritis, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真可惜  是的\N{\reng}Oh, that's a shame. Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她膝蓋有炎癥  只得退休了\N{\reng}It's in her knees now so that's her had to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,其實\N{\reng}It's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以在節假日工作  時薪八磅\N{\reng}Eight pound an hour, holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她說可以幫幫我的忙  也帶你去\N{\reng}Says she'll see you into it as a favour to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,當清潔工是嗎  是的  挺好\N{\reng}Cleaning, aye? Aye, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  你在想什麼\N{\reng}Why, what were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒在想什麼\N{\reng}Thinking? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼也沒想  我出門在外你不擔心嗎\N{\reng}I wasnae thinking. I've just got out. Don't you worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不擔心  我在想你的孩子\N{\reng}No, I wasnae. I was thinking about your kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去納什維爾\N{\reng}I'm going to Nashville.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好小心一點\N{\reng}Well, you better mind your tag doesnae
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,通過安檢的時候別露餡\N{\reng}go off when you're going through security.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,首先  我要去劇院  把工作拿回來\N{\reng}First thing I'm going down the Opry I'm gonna get my job back
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我會努力的\N{\reng}and I'm gonna work for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我不屬於這裏的\N{\reng}There's nothing for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裏我可以磨練手藝\N{\reng}There I can be honing my craft,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,每天晚上在外面肆無忌憚地傻笑\N{\reng}out gigging every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,磨練手藝\N{\reng}Honing your cra...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你為那個白日夢付出的代價還不夠嗎\N{\reng}Do you not think you've sacrificed enough for that fantasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我們做出的犧牲還不夠嗎\N{\reng}Have we all not sacrificed enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼就是白日夢了\N{\reng}How's it a fantasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我唯一擅長的  學做生意\N{\reng}It's the only thing I'm good at. Learn a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,上大學  你沒在聽\N{\reng}Go to college. You're not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管你做什麼  但你得搞點正事\N{\reng}I don't care what you do, but do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我會好好利用我的天賦的\N{\reng}I've got my talent and I'm gonna use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒看電視嗎\N{\reng}Have you not been watching telly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他們根本不缺會唱歌的人\N{\reng}There's no shortage of folk who can sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,當他們飛過水面回家時有一支\N{\reng}...a high, distinctive whistle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,離地面很高的獨特的哨子\N{\reng}as they fly home over the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\reng}Fuck's sake!
