Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.64,0:49:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,聽起來對你來說有點幼稚\N{\reng}That sounds a bit babyish for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.88,0:49:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,第二個關鍵階段\N{\reng}Key Stage 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.06,0:50:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛那麼做\N{\reng}Why are you doing that?
