Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.76,0:50:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,來  我帶你去睡覺\N{\reng}Here, I'll take you back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.16,0:51:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮  是給誰的\N{\reng}Those are nice. Who are they for?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.93,0:51:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這個給伊斯拉  這個給索娜\N{\reng}This one's for Isla and this one's for Shona.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.30,0:51:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,伊斯拉和索娜\N{\reng}Isla and Shona.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.63,0:51:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你的期中假快到了  你知道嗎\N{\reng}Yous have halfterm coming up. Do you know that?
