Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.17,0:51:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我們做什麼好呢\N{\reng}What will we do, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.97,0:51:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會離開幾天  去沙灘\N{\reng}We'll go away for a few days, to the beach.
