Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.28,0:51:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我們當時在\N{\reng}We went just before...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.72,0:51:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在你搬去和你奶奶住之前\N{\reng}just before yous moved in with your granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.92,0:51:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你當時想把貝殼都撿起來  記得嗎\N{\reng}You wanted to pick up all the shells. Remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.17,0:52:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我們為什麼不能見你\N{\reng}How come we weren't allowed to see you?
