Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.91,1:03:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你唱你的歌  拿你的錢\N{\reng}Sing your song, get your money,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.34,1:03:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,然後消失\N{\reng}then you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.30,1:03:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小林  跟上\N{\reng}Lyle, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.07,1:03:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可沒有一整天的時間\N{\reng}We haven't got all day.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.64,1:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,蘿茜  你去哪了  兄弟\N{\reng}Rosie! Where you been, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.46,1:03:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不見蹤影啊\N{\reng}Havenae seen hide nor hair of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.55,1:03:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  小不點呢  我一會兒進來\N{\reng}All right, wee man? I'll be in in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.33,1:04:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好吧  夥計\N{\reng}You all right, pal?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.56,1:04:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  你知道的  我改過自新了\N{\reng}Aye, you know, I'm brandnew.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.11,1:04:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,小林\N{\reng}Lyle?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.64,1:04:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫小林  五歲了\N{\reng}His name's Lyle. He's five.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.41,1:04:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他搖晃衣櫃時衣櫃翻倒壓在他身上\N{\reng}He swung on a wardrobe and it fell on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.55,1:04:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我想應該只是手臂受傷\N{\reng}I think it's just his arms that he's
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.50,1:04:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但頭可能也傷到了\N{\reng}hurt, but maybe his head as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.35,1:04:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  小林  介意我稍微看看嗎\N{\reng}Okay, Lyle, do you mind if I have a wee look?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.56,1:04:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的  她只是稍微檢查一下  好嗎\N{\reng}All right. She's gonna have a wee look, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.89,1:04:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,對什麼過敏嗎\N{\reng}Any allergies?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.31,1:04:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不  我認為沒有\N{\reng}No, I don't... I don't think so, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.06,1:04:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,織物類創可貼\N{\reng}Fabric plasters.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.96,1:04:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  嗯  他需要照個X光\N{\reng}Okay, um, we'll need to Xray him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.00,1:04:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚病人比較多\N{\reng}It's one of those nights some here,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.67,1:04:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你們可能要過一段時間才能等到醫生\N{\reng}so it might be a while until a doctor sees yous.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.00,1:04:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我要外婆\N{\reng}Okay. I want my granny.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.04,1:04:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜  安靜  我要外婆\N{\reng}Shh, shh... Please! I want my granny!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.14,1:04:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的  沒事的  我要外婆\N{\reng}It's okay, it's okay. I want my granny!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.91,1:05:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你是小林的媽媽嗎  我是\N{\reng}Are you Lyle's mum? Aye, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.08,1:05:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我是尤薩夫醫生  抱歉等這麼久\N{\reng}Dr Yousaf. I'm sorry about the wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.57,1:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係\N{\reng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.18,1:05:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,X光顯示沒有大問題  但需要打個石膏\N{\reng}The Xray looks fairly straightforward, but he'll need a cast.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.59,1:05:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們什麼時候可以回家\N{\reng}When can we go home?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.72,1:05:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,腫脹消退後才可以安石膏\N{\reng}We can't get the cast on until the swelling's come down,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.12,1:05:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要再觀察幾個小時\N{\reng}so we are looking at a couple more hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.53,1:05:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉今晚這麼折騰\N{\reng}I'm sorry it's been such a long night.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.73,1:05:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,媽的\N{\reng}Oh, fucking hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.15,1:06:08.49,Dejun,,0,0,0,,6個未接來電
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.53,1:06:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪  他還在睡覺\N{\reng}Where is he? He's still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.81,1:06:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我把這個帶回家\N{\reng}Right. I'll take this one home and
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.55,1:06:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你留在這兒陪小不點\N{\reng}you can stay here with the wee fella.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.48,1:06:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\reng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.16,1:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你那樣的生活安穩得不值得一過\N{\reng}What's for you will no' go by you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.33,1:06:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,也許在麵包店待20年對你來說已經足夠\N{\reng}Maybe 20 year in the baker's is enough
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.94,1:06:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不滿足\N{\reng}for you, but it's not enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.73,1:06:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,去給我倒杯茶  親愛的\N{\reng}Away and get me a wee cup of tea, darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.80,1:07:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你出什麼毛病了\N{\reng}What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.11,1:07:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是  我只是想讓你幫\N{\reng}I just... I just need you to help.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.68,1:07:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,幫幫我\N{\reng}Help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.55,1:07:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,幫你  幫你做什麼\N{\reng}Help you? Help you do what?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.98,1:07:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你去派對而把他留在這兒  是這樣嗎\N{\reng}Leave him here while you go to a party? Is that the plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.72,1:07:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道那位貴太太把你當成什麼\N{\reng}I don't know what this awf'y toffy woman thinks you are,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.66,1:07:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但要是她知道了真相  你什麼也得不到\N{\reng}but she wouldnae give you a brass farthing if she knew the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.26,1:07:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你還沒告訴她  對吧\N{\reng}You havenae even told her, have you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.30,1:07:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她連你有孩子了都一無所知\N{\reng}She doesnae even have a clue that you've got kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.58,1:07:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你到現在還不打算把他們當回事\N{\reng}If you're no' even prepared to acknowledge their existence,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.95,1:07:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你就徹底沒救了\N{\reng}there's no hope for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.71,1:07:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,對於他們也是一樣\N{\reng}And there's sure as hell none for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.72,1:07:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧  去納什維爾\N{\reng}Go. Go to Nashville.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.59,1:07:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,去做你想做的一切  來  親愛的\N{\reng}Do whatever it is you wanna do. Come on, darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.86,1:08:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去看看你的小兄弟\N{\reng}Let's go see your wee brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.85,1:09:02.06,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 我走進這間酒吧 ♪\N{\reng}♪ Well, I only came into this bar ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.29,1:09:05.73,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 只是為了聽一首悲傷的曲子 ♪\N{\reng}♪ To hear a sad song... ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.30,1:09:17.04,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 我不想和你在電話裏交談 ♪\N{\reng}♪ I couldn't get you on the phone ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.70,1:09:20.21,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 所以我讓它那樣響著 ♪\N{\reng}♪ So I let it ring ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.01,1:09:23.74,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 響了又響 ♪\N{\reng}♪ On and on ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.01,1:09:29.31,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 在一首孤獨的小夜曲裏 ♪\N{\reng}♪ In a lonesome serenade ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.69,1:09:43.13,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 或許我應該嘗試找個方法 ♪\N{\reng}♪ Maybe I should try to find a way ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.13,1:09:45.90,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 一點點地  解決它 ♪\N{\reng}♪ To kinda, sorta, maybe work it out ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.34,1:09:51.70,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,蘿絲琳  你去哪了\N{\reng}Rose Lynn! Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.71,1:09:54.11,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,上帝啊  我以為你放我鴿子了\N{\reng}Jesus Christ! I thought you were a noshow.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.11,1:09:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這聒噪地都讓我下不來台了\N{\reng}The band have had to talk me off a ledge.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.91,1:09:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起來很疲憊  你還好嗎\N{\reng}You look tired. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.08,1:10:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我感到  煥然一新\N{\reng}Oh, yeah, aye. I'm... brandnew.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.28,1:10:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好  那就好\N{\reng}Oh, good, good. Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.85,1:10:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧  我們走  你可把我嚇慘了\N{\reng}Come on, let's go. You gave me such a fright.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.15,1:10:09.22,DeMusic,,0,0,0,,♪ 兩桶威士忌 ♪\N{\reng}♪ And a doublebarrel whisky... ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.07,1:10:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\reng}Okay, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.10,1:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不久前  我家門前閃光一現\N{\reng}so, not long ago, a spark of light flew in through my door
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.71,1:10:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我知道我為什麼\N{\reng}and reminded me of why I fell in
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.25,1:10:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,會對格拉斯哥這座城市一見鍾情\N{\reng}love with Glasgow in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.15,1:10:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這個女孩  如同這座城市  不可思議\N{\reng}The girl, like the city, is gallus.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.95,1:10:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她很有趣  更重要的是她無所畏懼\N{\reng}She's funny and, above all else, she's completely fearless.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.89,1:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在你們的幫助下  她會去到納什維爾\N{\reng}And with your help, she's going to Nashville
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.16,1:10:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,去做她生而注定的事\N{\reng}to do what she was put on this earth to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.26,1:10:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我很榮幸認識她  並成為她的朋友\N{\reng}I'm so proud to know her and call her my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.27,1:10:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,女士們  先生們\N{\reng}Ladies and gentlemen, put your
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.49,1:10:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,請為羅斯·林·哈蘭鼓掌歡呼吧\N{\reng}hands together for RoseLynn Harlan!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.29,1:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好了嗎  開始吧\N{\reng}Okay? Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.16,1:11:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不好意思  可以給我\N{\reng}Sorsorsorry. Can you just give me...?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.23,1:12:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,給我  給我五分鐘嗎\N{\reng}Give me... give me five.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.41,1:12:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,出什麼事了\N{\reng}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.95,1:12:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,蘿絲琳\N{\reng}Rose Lynn?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.22,1:12:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  嘿\N{\reng}Hey? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.12,1:12:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,蘿絲琳  等一等\N{\reng}Rose Lynn, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.29,1:12:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼了  你在幹嘛  你要去哪\N{\reng}What's going on? What are you doing? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.59,1:12:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼了\N{\reng}What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.40,1:12:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  親愛的  怎麼了\N{\reng}Oh, darling. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.07,1:12:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道當你將目光投向我時\N{\reng}I don't know what... what you see
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.80,1:12:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到的  是不是我\N{\reng}when you look at me, but it isnae me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.87,1:12:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼  我不處於什麼巔峰期\N{\reng}What are you talking about? I'm not at the height of my powers.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.31,1:12:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是無拘無束  有太多\N{\reng}I'm not free and there's so,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.20,1:12:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太多羈絆我的事情\N{\reng}so much I can't undo.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.51,1:12:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我坐過牢\N{\reng}I can't undo going to the jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.38,1:12:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法忘記  向同我一樣無知的少女\N{\reng}I cannae undo chucking in heroin
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.52,1:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,去販賣海洛因  醉生夢死\N{\reng}to all they lasses in there already fucked from drugs.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.52,1:12:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道還有什麼嗎\N{\reng}And do you know what else I cannae undo?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.19,1:12:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個孩子\N{\reng}Having two kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.22,1:12:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,十八歲以前我生了兩個可愛的孩子\N{\reng}Two beautiful children before I was 18.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.93,1:13:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,薇諾娜八歲\N{\reng}Wynonna, she's eight,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.33,1:13:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,小林五歲  而我\N{\reng}and Lyle, he's five, and I...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.03,1:13:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我蹲了十二個月監獄  對他們不聞不問\N{\reng}I got 12 months in the jail and I left behind two kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.91,1:13:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  那才是真相\N{\reng}Yeah, that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.48,1:13:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是你面前的這些\N{\reng}Not this.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.35,1:13:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一樁樁  一件件\N{\reng}That, them.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.25,1:13:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所有我給你造成的錯覺\N{\reng}Everything I made you think I am...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.05,1:13:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都是假象\N{\reng}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.24,1:13:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起  我只是\N{\reng}Sorry, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.56,1:14:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,來\N{\reng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.50,1:14:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到那邊有一個島  一個島\N{\reng}I see an island over there. An island?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.31,1:14:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是個蛤蜊  你覺得你能打開它嗎\N{\reng}It's a clam. Do you think you can open it?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.10,1:15:19.10,Dejun,,0,0,0,,致力於幫助他人  給每一個人帶去溫暖
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.10,1:15:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哈倫女士\N{\reng}Miss Harlan?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.11,1:15:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  我會開心起來的  只是\N{\reng}I mean, I'll be happy just...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.36,1:15:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那就\N{\reng}All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.09,1:16:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 祝你生日快樂 ♪\N{\reng}♪ Happy birthday to you ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.57,1:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要許個願嗎\N{\reng}Did you make a wish?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.81,1:16:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你幫我許吧\N{\reng}You can have mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.31,1:16:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  第一份誰要\N{\reng}Right. Who's having the first slice, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.55,1:16:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我  好的\N{\reng}Me. Yeah? Good.
