Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.81,1:18:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但我從未想過要剝奪你的希望\N{\reng}but I never meant to take away your hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.91,1:18:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在說什麼\N{\reng}I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.65,1:18:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,生活可能有更多的可能性  可能沒有\N{\reng}Maybe there is more to life or maybe there isnae.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.92,1:18:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\reng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.32,1:18:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我到過最遠的地方就是杜恩\N{\reng}I've never been further than Dunoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.66,1:18:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但你應該出去看看\N{\reng}But you need to away and see.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.33,1:18:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\reng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.80,1:18:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法重新來過\N{\reng}I cannae start all that up again.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.47,1:18:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都結束了\N{\reng}It's finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.51,1:18:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我總是說如果我不用十五歲就開始工作\N{\reng}I always said I'd go to college
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.74,1:18:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我會去上大學的\N{\reng}if I hadnae had to go to work at 15.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.45,1:18:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,或者我本就會去\N{\reng}And I would have.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.75,1:18:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾想做一名藥劑師\N{\reng}I wanted to be a pharmacist.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.55,1:19:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,實際上\N{\reng}The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.96,1:19:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道是什麼阻止了我嗎\N{\reng}what was stopping me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.79,1:19:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在我生了你以後  我本可以去的\N{\reng}Even after I had you, I could have gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.40,1:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想為你著想  總比\N{\reng}But I think it was just easier for me to...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.94,1:19:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,總比為自己拚搏\N{\reng}to want things for you
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.27,1:19:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要容易的多\N{\reng}than to go after them for myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.61,1:19:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有那份勇氣\N{\reng}I hadnae the gumption.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.41,1:19:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我承認\N{\reng}That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.78,1:19:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但你\N{\reng}But you...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.32,1:19:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你有\N{\reng}you do.
